<body>
    <h1>Batch FTP Upload</h1><hr />
    <p>Items needed:<br />
        <ul>
            <li>Directory to find .csv's</li>
            <li>Name of summary file (e.g. "ClientFileSummary2016-02-26-10-02.csv")</li>
            <li>Process for generating summary file</li>
            <li>ftp host address</li>
            <li>ftp username/password</li>
            <li>ftp directory</li>
            <li>what to do with .csv's when finished (e.g. move to "2016" subfolder)</li>
            <li>selectable presets</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
</body>
